<%= render :partial => 'partials/public_email_header' %>

<tr>
  <tr>
    <td class="please_dont_reply"><strong>Please don't reply to this email.</strong></td>
  </tr>

  <td class="content padding">

    <h3 class="last-call">PLEASE READ: Ask an Expert has changed names and moved to a new system, and this question will not be answered. Please ask your question at <a href="https://ask2.extension.org/">Ask Extension</a>.</h3>

    <p>Hello,</p>
    <p>Thank you for taking your time to submit your question to the <%= link_to @group.name, group_url(@group.id) %> Ask an Expert group</p>
    <p>Unfortunately there is no one marked available in this group to answer your question at this time.</p>

    <p>You can <%= link_to("find and directly contact your local Extension institution", "http://articles.extension.org/main/partners")%>. You can also visit check this group's <%= link_to "homepage", group_url(@group.id) %> to check their answering availablity.</p>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="content padding question_block">
    <div class="question_title"><%= link_to(@question.title.html_safe, submitter_view_url(:fingerprint => @question.question_fingerprint)) -%></div>
    <div class="question_body"><%= format_text_for_display(@question.body) %></div>
  </td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="meta_details"><strong>Please don't reply to this email.</strong></td>
</tr>

<%= render :partial => 'partials/public_email_footer' %>
